sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Card, CardContent, Typography, Box, Chip, LinearProgress, Alert, Divider, Grid, List, ListItem, ListItemIcon, ListItemText, } from '@mui/material'; import { CheckCircle, Pending, Error, Analytics, Storage, Link, AccountBalanceWallet, Speed, EmojiEvents, Warning, Info, Nature, } from '@mui/icons-material'; const BlockchainStatus = ({ projectData, aiAnalysis, blockchainData }) => { const getStatusColor = (score) => { if (score >= 85) return 'success'; if (score >= 70) return 'warning'; if (score >= 55) return 'info'; return 'error'; }; const getStatusIcon = (status) => { switch (status) { case 'approved': return ; case 'requires_review': return ; case 'needs_improvement': return ; default: return ; } }; const getCategoryDescription = (category) => { switch (category) { case 'excellent': return 'Outstanding project quality with comprehensive data'; case 'good': return 'Good project quality meeting all requirements'; case 'acceptable': return 'Acceptable project quality with minor improvements needed'; case 'poor': return 'Project quality needs significant improvement'; default: return 'Project quality assessment pending'; } }; return ( 🔗 Blockchain Integration Status {/* Overall Project Status */} {getStatusIcon(projectData.current_status)} Project ID: {projectData.project_id} Status: {projectData.current_status.replace('_', ' ').toUpperCase()} {/* AI Analysis Results */} {aiAnalysis && ( 🤖 AI Verification Analysis Overall Score {aiAnalysis.overall_score}/100 Category: {aiAnalysis.category || 'Unknown'} {getCategoryDescription(aiAnalysis.category)} Detailed Scores {aiAnalysis.detailed_scores && Object.entries(aiAnalysis.detailed_scores).map(([key, scoreData]) => ( {key.replace('_', ' ').replace(/\b\w/g, l => l.toUpperCase())} {typeof scoreData === 'object' ? scoreData.score : scoreData}/100 ))} {/* Ecosystem Assessment */} {aiAnalysis.ecosystem_assessment && ( }> Ecosystem Assessment: {aiAnalysis.ecosystem_assessment.ecosystem_type} Location Suitable: {aiAnalysis.ecosystem_assessment.location_suitable ? 'Yes' : 'No'} | Expected Carbon Range: {aiAnalysis.ecosystem_assessment.expected_carbon_range?.join('-')} tCO2/ha/year )} {/* Recommendations */} {aiAnalysis.recommendations && aiAnalysis.recommendations.length > 0 && ( }> Recommendations: {aiAnalysis.recommendations.map((rec, index) => ( ))} )} {/* Warnings */} {aiAnalysis.warnings && aiAnalysis.warnings.length > 0 && ( }> Warnings: {aiAnalysis.warnings.map((warning, index) => ( ))} )} )} {/* Blockchain Status */} ⛓️ Blockchain Registration {blockchainData && blockchainData.registered ? ( }> Successfully Registered on Polygon Amoy Testnet Blockchain ID: {blockchainData.blockchain_id} {blockchainData.tx_hash && ( Transaction Hash: {blockchainData.tx_hash} )} Your project data is now permanently stored on the blockchain ) : ( }> Blockchain Registration Pending Projects with scores ≥70 are automatically registered on blockchain. {projectData.verification_score < 70 && ' Improve your project quality to enable blockchain registration.' } )} {/* Next Steps */} 📋 Next Steps {projectData.next_steps && projectData.next_steps.map((step, index) => ( ))} Estimated processing time: {projectData.estimated_processing_time} {/* Performance Metrics */} 🎯 Performance Overview IPFS Storage {projectData.blockchain?.registered ? 'Active' : 'Pending'} Blockchain {blockchainData?.registered ? 'Registered' : 'Pending'} AI Score {aiAnalysis?.category || 'Pending'} Status {projectData.current_status.replace('_', ' ')} ); }; export default BlockchainStatus;
